song_lyrics: Man bhāvaniyā ve Swāmīkī bānī mere man...
Prauḍh pratāp Shrī Hariko kahī ke,
Antar nyun na rahāvaniyāve... mere man 3
Akhanḍ Muni yah batiyā sunī ke,
title: Man bhāvaniyā ve Swāmīkī bānī mere man
